4.00	The_Listeners_(novel)	The Listeners (novel)	The Listeners is a science fiction novel by American author James Gunn. It centers on the search for interstellar communication and the effect that receipt of a message has. Although the search and the message are the unifying background of the novel, the chapters explore the personal effect of these events have on the lives of the characters.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/97/GunnListeners.jpg/200px-GunnListeners.jpg
